title: Are They Bad Dreams, Or Are They Bad Omens?
description:
You get a phone call from a friend saying that they had a terrible dream, where, for context purposes, you had an extreme death.
Our Executive Vice President, Cassie wonders if the news she got was just a bad dream or a bad omen.
